name: Mace Windu (V)
Lore: 'Senior Jedi Council member who maintains rigorous adherence to the Code. Sent Qui-Gon to Naboo to accompany the Queen and learn more about the mysterious ''dark warrior''.',
Text: 'Mace''s game text may not be canceled (except at Senate) and he may fire one weapon twice per battle. Boba Fett may not add battle destiny draws here. Immune to attrition.(Original concept by Zane Thorp - Texas State Winner 2004)(Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)',
